Package org.azeckoski.reflectutils.map

Interface Summary
OrderedMap<K,V> A map which keeps track of the order the entries are added and allows retrieval of entries in the order they were entered as well
Use ArrayOrderedMap or ConcurrentOrderedMap depending on your needs
 

Class Summary
ArrayOrderedMap<K,V> A map which keeps track of the order the entries are added and allows retrieval of entries in the order they were entered as well, this is NOT safe for multi-threaded access, this is backed by a HashMap and ArrayList
ConcurrentOrderedMap<K,V> A map which keeps track of the order the entries are added and allows retrieval of entries in the order they were entered as well, this is safe for multi-threaded access, this is backed by a ConcurrentHashMap and Vector
ConcurrentOrderedMap.Null
